    "(b) Active monitoring: Intervening or interacting with the AI system to obtain more information or influence its behavior. 11.",
    "Inverse monitoring (a) Inverse Monitoring by Software: Using AI or other software tools to monitor and assess the behavior of human users or operators. 12.",
    "Self-monitoring (a) Self-monitoring: Enabling AI systems to monitor their own behavior, performance, and safety, and to selfcorrect or adapt as needed 13.",
